        <h2>{{{page.title}}}</h2>
        <p>
          I am currently working with the College of the Arts and the Infinity Fabrication Lab
          at the University of Florida to rebuild and update their website. I have already implemented
          an updated calendar/scheduling system which students can use to reserve lab equipment. This
          system improves on their old website by being more scalable as the lab grows, and easier for
          lab employees to manage in the back-end.
        </p>
        <p>
          Future improvements include:
          <ul>
            <li>An automated 3D file upload flow. Students and clients will be able to upload
