            to end, and will receive an email when their printed model is ready to pick up at the lab.</li>
            <li>A charging system that automatically calculates and charges students on their school accounts for lab materials costs.
            Formerly lab employees had to carefully format text files by hand and upload them to be processed by a UF server process. This system
            will take care of that busy-work.</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
